<p class="spike-note">The framework's real glossary (ingested), rendered with per-term
anchors so definition-on-touch's "full entry →" resolves one link away (§4).</p>

<h1>Glossary</h1>

<dl class="glossary">
  {%- for entry in glossary %}
  <dt id="{{ entry.anchor }}" class="cjk"><strong>{{ entry.term }}</strong></dt>
  <dd class="cjk">{{ entry.html | safe }}</dd>
  {%- endfor %}
</dl>

